Author: citicoin
Title: [ANN][CITI] Citicoin | Scrypt | New | Coming Soon
Body: http://i.imgur.com/w8kXcnT.gif  Citicoin Coming soon   Citicoin (CITI) is a alternative Crypto currency and a Scrypt version of Bitcoin   Citicoin Scrypt Algo Total Supply: 21,000,000 (21 Million) Block Reward: 50 Citicoins Block Time: 10 Minutes Difficulty Re target: Every Block Reward halving interval: 210,000 blocks Citicoins already mined and in Public solitary confinement: 210,000 Citicoins (1%)    There are no confirmed dates of release at this moment and Citicoin is still in Development. You can look for updates via Citicoin twitter Page:  https://twitter.com/citicoins    There are opportunities for Development positions on all scales and sizes so if your are interested then feel free to make contact via PM.  Citicoin as a crypto currency will look to aspire in being an example in simplicity, continually being developed in every aspect not only by developers but developers of the community. Citicoin would like to be integrated into the latest development concepts and try and be at the forefront in not only being a crypto currency but a crypto currency which has a value for the people who use it.
